measurements.description: Sixty-eight delicate flowers on 17 up to 23-cm inflorescences; plant immaculate, 95 cm wide by 63 cm tall, grown in bark in a 30-cm plastic bulb pan; sepals narrow, lanceolate, rolled and recurved distally, white blushed lavender; petals full, porrect, recurved distally, undulate margins, white, heavily blushed lavender, midrib white; lip tubular, flaring, undulate distally, white overlaid yellow, veined magenta basally, magenta distal quarter, picotee; column white, anther cap white; substance medium; texture diamond dust; also received award 202455285.
